T1  - Equity sales in Belgian corporate groups: expropriation of minority shareholders? A clinical study
AU  - Buysschaert, An
AU  - Deloof, Marc
AU  - Jegers, Marc
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 10
IS  - 1
SP  - 81
EP  - 103
PY  - 2004
